	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you are an admin, you can of course do it in the admin panel by searching for the user, and directly cutting off their ability to show a sig. If you're not an admin, you can always use Firefox's Adblock extension.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


