<br />
<br />I used to visit a forum that let each user determine whether they wanted to view signatures forum-wide. It was a V-bulletin board though.  This is also an option in phpBB3. I'm not sure if there is a hack for phpBB2 to do this or not.
<br />
<br />If you are wanting to garner support by the userbase here to have the admin shut off the use of signatures as a whole on the forum (which I'm almost sure is an option in the admin panel), I don't think too many of us will have hurt feelings ; )

		

